Last year, West Virginians were paying $3.26 for gas.

Now, with President Trump back in the White House, they are only paying $2.85.

@POTUS is saving Americans money!

I am grateful that Aaron, a West Virginian who was detained in Venezuela, has safely returned home thanks to President Trump!

@POTUS is standing up for our country and looking out for the American people.

Welcome home, Aaron! https://t.co/ZvstdGGMrg
